// https://www.shadertoy.com/view/dstfzf asymmetric blocks compactified float, 2023 by jt
// float variant of https://www.shadertoy.com/view/mdcBR2 asymmetric blocks compactified
// based on https://www.shadertoy.com/view/Dt2GRz Recursive Irregular Blocks SDF

// Attempt to compactify the pattern of
// random-blocks-by-alternating-double-T-crossings
// (aka asymmetric/irregular)
// Calculates only essential hashes.
// Basic documentation.
// This implementation is intended for lookup with floats.
// Click to show underlying grid.

// NOTE: integer hash for comparison with integer version
//       (can be changed by uncommenting line in block_hash)

// integer variant:
// https://www.shadertoy.com/view/mdcBR2 asymmetric blocks compactified

// tags: random, t, blocks, double, alternating, irregular, asymmetric

